methods.equals:
Helper method for implementing Object.equals(Object).

:param aArray: (io.deephaven.vector.CharVector) - The LHS of the equality test (always a CharVector)
:param b: (java.lang.Object) - The RHS of the equality test
:return: (boolean) Whether the two inputs are equal
methods.getDirect:
Return a version of this Vector that is flattened out to only reference memory.

:return: io.deephaven.vector.CharVector
methods.hashCode:
Helper method for implementing Object.hashCode(). Follows the pattern in
 Arrays.hashCode(Object[]).

:param array: (io.deephaven.vector.CharVector) - The CharVector to hash
:return: (int) The hash code
methods.size:
The size of this data structure.

:return: (long) The size
methods.toString:
Helper method for implementing Object.toString().

*Overload 1*  
  :param prefixLength: int
  :return: java.lang.String
  
*Overload 2*  
  :param array: (io.deephaven.vector.CharVector) - The CharVector to convert to a String
  :param prefixLength: (int) - The maximum prefix of the array to convert
  :return: (java.lang.String) The String representation of array
